687
01:08:08,386 --> 01:08:11,184
- What?
- I don't want to go to the dentist.

688
01:08:11,355 --> 01:08:13,983
- Why not?
- I just don't want to go.

689
01:08:14,158 --> 01:08:16,388
- What, are you scared?
- No.

690
01:08:18,296 --> 01:08:20,161
We're gonna reschedule, though.

691
01:08:20,331 --> 01:08:24,563
Tell you what, I'll let you play hooky
if you want to come and draw with me.

692
01:08:24,735 --> 01:08:26,669
All right.

693
01:08:30,341 --> 01:08:32,036
Wait, Daniel.

694
01:08:32,209 --> 01:08:35,667
How are you two getting along
with Esther?

695
01:08:38,182 --> 01:08:39,342
