696
01:08:39,517 --> 01:08:40,848
Yeah?
Yeah, Mom.

697
01:08:43,154 --> 01:08:47,181
But has she ever made you feel,
I don't know, uncomfortable...

698
01:08:47,358 --> 01:08:50,350
...or has she done anything
that she's not supposed to do?

699
01:08:51,362 --> 01:08:55,492
- No.
- Like, has she ever hurt any of you?

700
01:08:56,634 --> 01:08:58,226
No.

701
01:09:01,772 --> 01:09:03,171
You sure?

702
01:09:06,644 --> 01:09:09,738
Okay. All right.

703
01:09:11,349 --> 01:09:13,943
I like it when it's just the two of us.

704
01:09:14,151 --> 01:09:18,212
You don't know how long I've waited
for a daddy just like you.

705
01:09:18,389 --> 01:09:19,856
Mommy too, right?

706
01:09:21,859 --> 01:09:23,724
I don't think
Mommy likes me very much.

707
01:09:23,894 --> 01:09:25,293
Hey.

708
01:09:25,463 --> 01:09:28,023
- That is not true. Mommy loves you.
- It's all right.

709
01:09:28,199 --> 01:09:31,293
It must be hard to love an adopted child
as much as your own.

710
01:09:31,469 --> 01:09:35,929
Sweetheart, you're just as much a part
of this family as Danny and Max. Okay?

711
01:09:37,041 --> 01:09:40,272
Do something nice for Mommy.
Show her how much you love her.

712
01:09:40,444 --> 01:09:42,969
That's a wonderful idea.

713
01:10:02,600 --> 01:10:04,761
I have a special surprise
for you, Mommy.

714
01:10:05,736 --> 01:10:07,135
You do?

715
01:10:08,773 --> 01:10:11,503
I picked these flowers just for you.

716
01:10:14,478 --> 01:10:20,439
- Esther, what did you do? God.
My arm!

717
01:10:20,618 --> 01:10:21,983
Why did you do this?
- Daddy, my arm!

718
01:10:23,721 --> 01:10:24,847
John!
- Hey.

719
01:10:25,022 --> 01:10:28,014
What did you do?
Hey. Stop, stop.

720
01:10:28,225 --> 01:10:29,283
Why did you do this?

721
01:10:29,460 --> 01:10:32,520
- Oh, God. God, she did this on purpose.
- No, no, no.

722
01:10:32,730 --> 01:10:34,163
- Yes, she did.
- Hey. Honey, no.

723
01:10:34,331 --> 01:10:36,765
She knew
what these roses meant to me.

724
01:10:36,934 --> 01:10:40,267
It's my fault, hon. I told her
to do something nice for you.

725
01:10:40,438 --> 01:10:42,133
I can't believe this.

726
01:12:24,341 --> 01:12:26,605
Daddy!

727
01:12:27,344 --> 01:12:29,608
Daddy!

728
01:12:30,748 --> 01:12:33,239
Daddy, Daddy!

729
01:12:33,417 --> 01:12:34,475
What is it, honey?

730
01:12:35,119 --> 01:12:37,280
My arm still hurts.

731
01:12:42,226 --> 01:12:45,662
Can I have a look at it?
You're okay.

732
01:12:45,863 --> 01:12:48,297
I'll be gentle. It's all right, honey.

733
01:12:48,465 --> 01:12:50,228
Oh, my God.

734
01:12:52,102 --> 01:12:54,593
We need to take you to the hospital.

735
01:12:59,176 --> 01:13:01,610
You're a brave little girl,
you know that?

736
01:13:01,779 --> 01:13:04,577
Doctor said
you're gonna heal real fast, okay?

737
01:13:21,098 --> 01:13:22,292
You broke her arm.

738
01:13:26,403 --> 01:13:28,530
It's impossible.
I didn't grab her that hard.

739
01:13:28,706 --> 01:13:33,803
She wants to sleep in here tonight.
Maybe you should sleep downstairs.

740
01:13:53,731 --> 01:13:56,165
I'm having guests for dinner.

741
01:14:00,304 --> 01:14:03,000
You know, you can have it. Thanks.

742
01:15:06,403 --> 01:15:08,633
Have a good day.

743
01:15:16,547 --> 01:15:18,139
Daniel.

744
01:15:18,315 --> 01:15:20,044
Your books.

745
01:15:23,554 --> 01:15:26,819
- What happened? Let me see your bag.
- I don't know.

746
01:15:29,093 --> 01:15:32,585
We just bought this.
Pick it up, it's gonna get wet.

747
01:15:39,169 --> 01:15:40,830
Mom!

748
01:15:43,040 --> 01:15:46,271
Max! No! Help!

749
01:15:47,778 --> 01:15:49,575
Max!

750
01:15:51,348 --> 01:15:52,906
Max!

751
01:16:05,262 --> 01:16:06,820
Max!

752
01:16:14,338 --> 01:16:16,203
Max!

753
01:16:16,373 --> 01:16:18,136
Are you okay?

754
01:16:18,308 --> 01:16:21,675
I'm here. Mommy's here.
You're okay, honey. Come on.

755
01:16:21,845 --> 01:16:26,805
I got you. Yeah. Oh, baby, it's okay.
I'm so sorry.

756
01:16:28,852 --> 01:16:31,343
I remember I put it in park
and I set the brake.

