01:39:42,777 --> 01:39:47,441
She has a rare hormone disorder.
It's called hypopituitarism.

1000
01:39:47,615 --> 01:39:50,584
It causes proportional dwarfism.
She only looks like a child.

1001
01:39:51,119 --> 01:39:56,386
According to our records,
Leena Klammer was born in 1976.

1002
01:39:56,558 --> 01:39:58,526
She's 33 years old.

1003
01:39:58,693 --> 01:40:01,093
This can't be. This is a mistake.

1004
01:40:01,262 --> 01:40:04,459
<i>I hope so, for your sake.
Does she have the scars?</i>

1005
01:40:04,632 --> 01:40:07,294
What? I don't know. What scars?

1006
01:40:07,502 --> 01:40:09,902
Leena was one
of our most violent patients.

1007
01:40:10,071 --> 01:40:12,562
When she was here,
she was kept in a straitjacket...

1008
01:40:12,740 --> 01:40:14,571
<i>...to stop her from hurting our staff.</i>

1009
01:40:14,742 --> 01:40:16,733
<i>She was constantly fighting
to get out.</i>

1010
01:40:16,911 --> 01:40:21,939
<i>It cut into her skin and left her
with scars around her wrists and neck.</i>

1011
01:40:22,116 --> 01:40:24,414
<i>There is no way
you could not have seen them.</i>

1012
01:40:24,586 --> 01:40:26,053
Why was she at your hospital?

1013
01:40:26,221 --> 01:40:30,658
<i>She's dangerously ill, violent.
She killed seven people that we know of.</i>

1014
01:40:30,825 --> 01:40:33,623
Oh, my God. How could she fool us?

1015
01:40:33,795 --> 01:40:37,458
<i>She has been passing herself off
as a little girl for most of her life.</i>

1016
01:40:38,132 --> 01:40:41,158
<i>She tricked a family here in Estonia
into adopting her.</i>

1017
01:40:41,336 --> 01:40:46,330
When she couldn't seduce the father,
she killed him and his whole family.

1018
01:40:46,541 --> 01:40:50,068
<i>- Then she burned the house down.
- Yes. How did you know?</i>

1019
01:40:50,245 --> 01:40:53,305
She disappeared a year ago
and we lost track of her.

1020
01:40:53,481 --> 01:40:56,541
<i>If it's really Leena,
you don't have much time.</i>

1021
01:41:37,659 --> 01:41:39,388
Esther?

1022
01:42:53,234 --> 01:42:56,294
Come on, Johnny. Come on.
Pick up the fucking phone.

1023
01:43:06,814 --> 01:43:08,611
Shit.

1024
01:43:30,505 --> 01:43:32,234
Come on.

1025
01:43:33,708 --> 01:43:34,902
Oh, God!

1026
01:44:07,341 --> 01:44:08,774
Come on.

1027
01:44:12,313 --> 01:44:13,337
Come on.

1028
01:44:13,514 --> 01:44:15,209
