1033
01:45:00,928 --> 01:45:02,293
Oh, fuck it.

1034
01:46:18,873 --> 01:46:20,568
John?

1035
01:46:25,746 --> 01:46:28,806
John? John?

1036
01:46:30,918 --> 01:46:33,512
No, God!

1037
01:46:45,666 --> 01:46:47,497
No, God!

1038
01:46:50,538 --> 01:46:51,903
Max.

1039
01:48:31,806 --> 01:48:33,637
What the fuck?

1040
01:51:04,525 --> 01:51:07,255
Esther! Don't you hurt her!

1041
01:51:12,867 --> 01:51:15,802
Leave her alone! I'm here!

1042
01:51:16,804 --> 01:51:18,396
Esther!

1043
01:52:48,963 --> 01:52:50,260
I know.

1044
01:54:45,679 --> 01:54:48,671
Go back. It's too dangerous. Go back.

1045
01:55:02,329 --> 01:55:04,263
Please.

1046
01:55:04,431 --> 01:55:06,524
Don't let me die, Mommy.

1047
01:55:10,037 --> 01:55:13,598
I'm not your fucking Mommy!

1048
01:55:29,623 --> 01:55:31,853
Baby, it's okay.

